<!-- ── Why pay at all ── -->
<section>
    <div class="container">
        <p class="section-label reveal">
            Why the free tier works the way it does
        </p>
        <p class="section-lead reveal">
            A retrieve is the moment the product delivers on its promise – a thought you captured finds you
            at exactly the right moment.
            The free tier gives you twenty of those moments.
            Twenty retrieves across different cue types gives you a genuine picture of what the product does
            before you spend anything.
            You pay only after you've seen it work.
        </p>
        <p class="section-lead reveal">
            The paywall appears after your twentieth retrieve – not after you've captured twenty thoughts,
            not on a timer, not before you've had a chance to explore.
            At the right moment, like everything else Captrieve does.
        </p>
    </div>
</section>

